## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Install Dioxus CLI
cargo install dioxus-cli

# New project (auto-detect template)
dx new my-dioxus-app

# Development
cd my-dioxus-app
dx serve

# Build specific platform
dx build --platform web
dx build --platform desktop
dx build --platform mobile

# Fullstack with server functions
dx serve --fullstack
```

---

## 📊 Quick Reference

| Concept | Dioxus | React | Leptos |
|---------|--------|-------|--------|
| **Component** | `fn App() -> Element` | `function App()` | `fn App() -> impl IntoView` |
| **State** | `use_signal()` | `useState()` | `create_signal()` |
| **Effect** | `use_effect()` | `useEffect()` | `create_effect()` |
| **Memo** | `use_memo()` | `useMemo()` | `create_memo()` |
| **Resource** | `use_resource()` | `useQuery()` | `create_resource()` |

